        <%=image_tag "shorewood_clinc.jpg", class: "img-fluid picture" %>
        <h2>Meet the Coach</h2>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-5 mx-auto">
          <blockquote><q><i>The foundation of a good coaching relationship is getting to know each other. An athlete must trust their coach and a coach must believe in the athlete.</i></q><p class="text-right">-Coach Joe</p></blockquote>
